{"tid":1577442,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"必睇！應對惡狗盜用烈士連登帳戶嘅妙法，請連仔隔幾日要求會員在開戶電郵再激活帳戶","createTime":"2019-09-17T16:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T17:18:53.000Z","uid":271434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3d13dff4eab4c903ab095147a1aa7729a6fa1c","tid":1577442,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前估計已經有大量連登仔帳戶因被拘捕、被虐殺而流到黑勢力，散佈大量謠言，影響運動風向，我有以下妙計：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應對有人偷義士連登ac方法：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">強烈要求連仔隔幾日send email去開戶電郵要求用家激活，先可以繼續出post及睇加密內容，否則暫停出post及回post權利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">另外，因權限問題無法今日再開新貼。<br />\n由於有高人指烈士冤魂暫不接受超渡，同埋唔願意去投胎，佢地將會繼續受到非常大嘅痛苦。<span style=\"color: gold;\">希望有法力嘅人士幫手，俾為民主殉道嘅全部義士可以升為香港城隍</span>，等佢地過得好啲，同埋讓佢地獲得更大權力，繼續為香港人主持公道，懲惡除奸。</span><br />\n<br />\n參考文字：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWaNXAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWaNXAX.png&h=07a79237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參考網站：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/211597766316250?view=permalink&amp;id=542077126601644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F211597766316250%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D542077126601644&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5BZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=ff50c79e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/211597766316250?view=permalink&amp;id=542077126601644</a>"},{"pid":"ccf57e64d29cfb4a7d828ac025aae6394c41ab16","tid":1577442,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"另外請大家幫推我嘅優質post：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核彈！中共極懼怕網絡信息安全在國慶節前出事！兄弟們即刻行動香港可獲